overview: It's spring 1984. Doug's only concerned with the newest Star Trek movie and escaping high school as quick as he can, when he's faced with his worst nightmare: Prom. Noisy crowds, loud music, a pushy sister and bullies, all in one place. To make matters worse, there's a horrific mutant monster trying to eat as many kids as it can.
tagline: Just when they thought this night couldn't get any worse
title: Wost Prom Ever
